SIMPLE: hourly
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hourly
<hw>Hour"ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Happening or done
every hour; occurring hour by hour; frequent; often repeated; renewed
hour by hour; continual.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In <qex>hourly</qex> expectation of a martyrdom.</q>
<rj><qau>Sharp.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hourly</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Hourly
<hw>Hour"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Every hour; frequently;
continually.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Great was their strife, which <qex>hourly</qex> was renewed.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hours</ent>⟦br⟧
